  "title": "Sales Executive (Japanese Account)",
  "description": "<p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Manage existing accounts and establish new customer’s account by cold calling and canvassing. </li><li>Conduct sales presentation and prepare sales proposals for sales closure to meet the company’s sales and profit targets. </li><li>Conduct product demonstration and training to end users. </li><li>Develop and maintain strong relationship with the customers for business growth. </li><li>Analyze customer’s business environment and propose suitable workflow and document management solutions. </li></ul><p><strong></strong><br /><strong>REQUIREMENTS </strong></p><ul><li>Possess Degree in Sales & Marketing or equivalent.</li><li>Proficient in conversational and written business Japanese, delivering sales presentations and preparing sales proposals for Japanese-speaking customers and colleagues.</li><li>Preferably, with relevant direct sales experience in Digital Multi-Functional Copier or Business Equipment Product. </li><li>Good communication and presentation skills. </li><li>Resourceful, self-motivated and result-oriented. </li><li>Customer-service mind-set and possess strong interpersonal skills. </li><li>Good knowledge of Microsoft Office program (e.g., Words, Excel and PowerPoint). </li></ul>",
